Village, and I'm here today to talk to you

00:00:03.180 --> 00:00:08.721
about playing chords on a keyboard. A lot
of people have the misconception that a lot

00:00:08.721 --> 00:00:14.170
of keyboardists will play a style that was
really popular in the '70s with a Hammond

00:00:14.170 --> 00:00:19.330
