a lot of quick fingering on the keyboard and

00:00:19.330 --> 00:00:26.829
will play fast trills or fast-moving notes,
they would solo a lot, and not all keyboardists

00:00:26.829 --> 00:00:32.520
have to do that. In fact, when I play keyboard
most of the time, I sit and I play chords.

00:00:32.520 --> 00:00:37.430
What most people think of when they hear about
keyboards especially from back in the day,

00:00:37.430 --> 00:00:57.190
they hear more melodic-sounding stuff that
would sound something like this.

00:00:57.190 --> 00:01:03.710
