use that if you are going to be soloing but

00:01:03.710 --> 00:01:09.180
a lot of times, keyboardists really don't
do that. And so, what I do is I will play

00:01:09.180 --> 00:01:14.360
a lot of chords and that comes from years
and years of practicing piano and keyboards

00:01:14.360 --> 00:01:51.659
but there are many different chords that you
can use.

00:01:51.659 --> 00:01:56.799
So, it's important to decide what needs to
fit into your piece, what needs to fit into

00:01:56.799 --> 00:02:00.659
